"date":"July 28, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Abbas reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cTwo supplications have no barrier between them and Allah: the supplication of the oppressed, and the supplication of a man for his brother behind his back.\u201d Source: al-Mu\u2019jam al-Kabi\u0304r lil-T\u0323abara\u0304ni\u0304 11232 Grade:\u00a0Sahih\u00a0(authentic) according to Al-Suyuti \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0650\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":23208,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2016\/06\/14\/dua-oppressed-ascends-heaven\/","url_meta":{"origin":36125,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Dua: Supplication of oppressed ascends to heaven","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 14, 2016","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Umar reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cBeware of the supplication of the oppressed, for it ascends to the heavens as if it were a flare.\u201d Source: al-Mustadrak \u2018ala\u0301 al-S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323ayn 81 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0650 \u0627\u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0639\u064f\u0645\u064e\u0631\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":34174,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2020\/05\/03\/three-people-always-answered\/"